{"tid":2036477,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於聽日嘅行動，我有少少嘢想講。","createTime":"2020-05-26T13:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T13:50:00.000Z","uid":292433,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab510966caf96de760152856df91d346c561b688","tid":2036477,"uid":292433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人，係時候理性啲咁諗吓，行動可唔可行、風險高唔高。我知如果淨係靠理性嘅話，我哋無可能行到今日，但係我哋嘅抗爭唔係一日嘅事、手法唔係得一種。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「Be water 」</strong>&mdash; 唔係叫你乜都唔做，喺屋企嘆冷氣，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而係每一次行動都要改善，唔係死守一個地方。</span>問心嗰句，你覺得有無機會重現612？好多和理非已經驚咗，好多手足已經紅牌出場，淨係講人數，我哋已經無咗好多。再講，依家我哋連金鐘都入唔去，你喺黑警格離行過，佢都可以槍殺你，揸車撞你。更何況，當林奠講撤回嘅時候，我哋失去咗嘅已經太多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「勇氣智慧也永不滅」</strong>&mdash; 我哋一開始行出嚟已經係好有勇氣嘅表現，仲要支持到今日，真係好叻。我哋試過包圍立會、快閃開花、去機場、全球登報等等，仲有其他國家嘅示威者參考我哋嘅做法，呢啲就係智慧嘅表現。<br />\n<br />\n文筆好差，但我想大家諗吓，惡歌法後面仲有国安法、23條，我哋阻到佢開會幾多次。更何況中共繞過立會直接立法都得啦。<strong>我唔想再由中共港共lead住我哋嚟行，我唔想再跟住佢哋嘅劇本嚟行。當然，街頭抗爭係不可缺少嘅一環，但係我哋係咪仲要原地踏步呢？</strong><br />\n<br />\n我唔係想散播失敗主義，只係想大家有獨立思考，唔好再英雄主義/浪漫化抗爭。Sorry for 1999，第一次出po，屌細力啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a3e5cd10699580374d3340e29ddbf7f93c688a","tid":2036477,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"[文長慎入]中共已經｢哂冷｣，香港人選擇下注還是下跪？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2029861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2029861</a>"},{"pid":"1609b9be49610d19901ac1907893afe70d127d44","tid":2036477,"uid":292433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:23:23.000Z","msg":"不過點都好啦，只要有手足行出嚟，我都會照樣行出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c80ad97f7ed55cbdc5a2ed4b08e4d0733f77f55","tid":2036477,"uid":292433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民族自強 香港獨立</span>"},{"pid":"07fe526b57768f3adf961a3713762b9b1736a870","tid":2036477,"uid":292433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:35:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span>"},{"pid":"59f4f6b3746bb70d5e5e4be2a27eae276201ced2","tid":2036477,"uid":292433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:36:57.000Z","msg":"點解無人睇㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1e3c79167cefcba0a5d4695edeb4b0322178ef","tid":2036477,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"因為我地都係p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a49ecc509ff805ff1dd99719f270e007ec24c4","tid":2036477,"uid":292433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa1e3c79167cefcba0a5d4695edeb4b0322178ef","tid":2036477,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"因為我地都係p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113a544cee061a0e9ee4324701003d81579ef4f6","tid":2036477,"uid":292433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:50:00.000Z","msg":"最緊要 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小心 冷靜 平安</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}